  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies the color primaries according to ITU-T H.273 CICP (Coding-independent Code Points).</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKColorspacePrimariesCicp` specifies the color primaries of a color space using the CICP (Coding-independent Code Points) system defined in ITU-T H.273. Use these values with <see cref="M:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp" /> to create a color space with a specific color gamut.

## Examples

```csharp
// Create an sRGB color space using CICP parameters
var colorSpace = SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(
    SKColorspacePrimariesCicp.Rec709,
    SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp.Iec6196621);
```
]]></format></remarks>
